genresAdvancedInfo.name: senegalese traditional
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Senegalese traditional music is a diverse genre that encompasses many different styles and traditions. From the griot storytelling tradition to the sabar drumming style, Senegalese traditional music is deeply rooted in the country's history and culture. The music often features a mix of traditional instruments like the kora and the balafon, as well as modern instruments like the guitar and keyboard.
